%% Gambar I.2 / III.x - Alur uji pendahuluan menuju eksperimen utama
%% Type: BPMN-style decision process.
%% Reference basis: OMG BPMN 2.0.2; implementation evidence from APE workspace.
flowchart TB
    plan[Desain penelitian dua tahap]
    pilot[Uji pendahuluan: REST vs GraphQL pada skenario awal]
    pilotMetrics[Metrik pilot: latency, throughput, payload, processing time, CPU, RSS]
    evaluate[Evaluasi kesiapan instrument dan variabilitas hasil]
    calibrate[Kalibrasi desain eksperimen utama]
    main[Eksperimen utama Phase 2]
    controls[Kontrol utama: shared DAL, SQLite MOT corpus, APQ-over-GET, Varnish, access pattern, entropy, payload weight, network profile]
    analysis[Analisis hasil utama per experimental cell]

    plan --> pilot --> pilotMetrics --> evaluate --> calibrate --> main --> controls --> analysis
